{"tid":1046073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"的士法正式刊登90日後生效 的士必須安裝衛星定位錄音及錄影設備加強打擊黑的","createTime":"2019-03-04T03:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T13:17:46.000Z","uid":54373,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"397cac1d491068a3f9c4af391bc1d4bb32a69247","tid":1046073,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T03:18:35.000Z","msg":"（今日出版的特區公報正式刊登的士法律制度。）<br />\n<br />\n今（4）日特區公報正式刊登《輕型出租汽車客運法律制度》，法律將於公布後滿90日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n該法律於上月19日獲立法會細則性審議通過。新法提升的士司機違規行為罰款金額，司機若5年內4次違規（包括拒載、濫收車資等），將會被取消的士駕駛員證。新法又規定須有500萬註冊資本公司方可競投的士牌照，同時的士內須安裝衛星定位、錄音及錄影設備，以加強對不法司機阻嚇及打擊力度。"},{"pid":"c00a7310632a4310b95d49a83ee6d585eef494f0","tid":1046073,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:21:18.000Z","msg":"的士狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674605eabc36d70ae031713be82eb491f9537b49","tid":1046073,"uid":197337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:27:23.000Z","msg":"有500萬註冊資本公司方可競投的士牌照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed77dd2ba0d643cdd8d11178ea1e24a0b1d6728","tid":1046073,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:29:01.000Z","msg":"跟著又話無私穩屌三屌四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf7a2e9d1f1fdef23c64eb927c21e7efb9ea505","tid":1046073,"uid":21139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:29:17.000Z","msg":"澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15ca92777f9f65b6c41771954c8c8945433a7b4","tid":1046073,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟著又話無私隱屌三屌四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fd006e226f2008cf578d12e049c1d79138244a5b","tid":1046073,"uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"